{"metadata":{"kernelspec":{"name":"ir","display_name":"R","language":"R"},"language_info":{"name":"R","codemirror_mode":"r","pygments_lexer":"r","mimetype":"text/x-r-source","file_extension":".r","version":"4.0.5"}},"nbformat_minor":4,"nbformat":4,"cells":[{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"### Intorduction\nThis time the competition seems to be about stock price forecasts.  \nI would like to check for information that may be relevant to the movement of stock prices.  \nI will also leave the information in Japanese so that it can be easily reviewed later .\n  \n私は株価の動きに関連しそうな情報についてしらべていきたいと思います。  \nあとで見直ししやすいようにもとの日本語も残すようにします。","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"code","source":"options(warn=-1)\nlibrary(tidyverse) # metapackage of all tidyverse packages\nsuppressPackageStartupMessages(library(data.table))\nsuppressPackageStartupMessages(library(scales))\nsuppressPackageStartupMessages(library(patchwork)) # Multiple graphs can be easily arranged.  \nsuppressPackageStartupMessages(library(lemon)) # lemon is also usefull!\nsuppressPackageStartupMessages(library(lubridate))\n#suppressPackageStartupMessages(library(magick)) # Show images\n\n#ggplot setting\ntheme_set(theme_minimal() +\n         theme(plot.title = element_text(size = 17, face = \"bold\"),\n               plot.subtitle = element_text(size = 15, face = \"bold\"),\n               axis.text.x = element_text(size = 15),\n               axis.text.y = element_text(size = 15),\n               axis.title.x = element_text(size = 18),\n               axis.title.y = element_text(size = 18),\n               legend.text = element_text(size = 15),\n               legend.title = element_text(size = 15),\n               strip.text.x = element_text(size = 15)\n              )\n          )\n\n#Choose your favorite color\nmycol = c(\"turquoise\", \"lightslateblue\",\"lightskyblue\", \n          \"chartreuse2\", \"palegreen2\", \"mistyrose2\", \"grey60\", \"hotpink1\")","metadata":{"_uuid":"8f2839f25d086af736a60e9eeb907d3b93b6e0e5","_cell_guid":"b1076dfc-b9ad-4769-8c92-a6c4dae69d19","_kg_hide-input":true,"execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2022-04-30T02:43:24.344388Z","iopub.execute_input":"2022-04-30T02:43:24.346884Z","iopub.status.idle":"2022-04-30T02:43:26.010315Z"},"trusted":true},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"code","source":"#show_col(mycol)","metadata":{"_kg_hide-input":true,"execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2022-04-30T02:43:26.012809Z","iopub.execute_input":"2022-04-30T02:43:26.06357Z","iopub.status.idle":"2022-04-30T02:43:26.075069Z"},"trusted":true},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"## Data files\n* There seems to be \"stock_list\" file on the level above the training data.\n* \"stock_list\" probably contains information on stocks in the Tokyo market.  \n* stock_listというファイルがトレーニングホルダーの上位にあります。\n* これは東京市場の基本情報のファイルと思われます。","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"code","source":"data_path = \"../input/jpx-tokyo-stock-exchange-prediction/\"\ntrain_path = paste0(data_path, \"train_files/\")\ncat(\"list of the top directry\")\nlist.files(data_path, full.names = T)\ncat(\"training_data\")\nlist.files(train_path, full.names = T)","metadata":{"execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2022-04-30T02:43:26.077601Z","iopub.execute_input":"2022-04-30T02:43:26.079044Z","iopub.status.idle":"2022-04-30T02:43:26.121254Z"},"trusted":true},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"code","source":"#===== Data loading =====\n\nstock_list <- fread(paste0(data_path, \"stock_list.csv\"),\n                    na.strings = c(\"\",\"NULL\"))\nstock_prices <- fread(paste0(train_path, \"stock_prices.csv\"),\n                      na.strings = c(\"\",\"NULL\"))\nfinancials <- fread(paste0(train_path, \"financials.csv\"),\n                    na.strings = c(\"\",\"NULL\"))\n","metadata":{"execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2022-04-30T02:43:26.123648Z","iopub.execute_input":"2022-04-30T02:43:26.125052Z","iopub.status.idle":"2022-04-30T02:43:32.209725Z"},"trusted":true},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"## stock_list\n\n**This is assumed to be information on all issues in the Tokyo market.**  \n**東京市場の全銘柄情報と思われます。**  \n  \nThen, check the column names.  \nまず、列名称をチェックします。","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"code","source":"names(stock_list)","metadata":{"execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2022-04-30T02:43:32.212351Z","iopub.execute_input":"2022-04-30T02:43:32.213808Z","iopub.status.idle":"2022-04-30T02:43:32.229706Z"},"trusted":true},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"* Some column names may need to be changed.\n* いくつか列名称を変更する必要がありそうです。","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"**Let's change the column names and take a quick look at the data.**","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"code","source":"st1 <- names(stock_list)[str_detect(names(stock_list), \"^[0-9]\")]\nst2 <- c(\"SectorCode_33\", \"SectorName_33\", \"SectorCode_17\", \"SectorName_17\")\nsetnames(stock_list, st1, st2)\n\nst1 <- names(stock_list)[str_detect(names(stock_list), \"/\")] %>% \nstr_replace_all(\"/\", \"_\")\nsetnames(stock_list, names(stock_list)[str_detect(names(stock_list), \"/\")], st1)\n\nglimpse(stock_list)","metadata":{"_kg_hide-input":true,"execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2022-04-30T02:43:32.232207Z","iopub.execute_input":"2022-04-30T02:43:32.233593Z","iopub.status.idle":"2022-04-30T02:43:32.295124Z"},"trusted":true},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"**A quick look at the above and I think the following are likely to be relevant to the price movement of the stock.**  \n1. Section_Products: probably a traditional market segment  \n1. NewMarketSegment: New market segment from 2022/04/04  \n1. SectorCode_33: 33 sector classification  \n1. SectorCode_17: 17 sector classification  \n  \n* Growth market stocks are expected to have large price movements.  \n* Similar price movements are expected for stocks in the same sector.\n  \n  \n**上記をぱっとみて、株の値動きに関連しそうなのは以下と思います。**  \n1. Section_Products: おそらく従来の市場区分  \n1. NewMarketSegment: 2022/04/04 からの新市場区分  \n1. SectorCode_33: 33セクター分類  \n1. SectorCode_17: 17セクター分類  \n  \n* 成長市場銘柄は値動きが大きいことが予想されます。  \n* 同一セクター銘柄は同じような値動きになることが予想されます。","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"**Generate the list of unique_values**","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"code","source":"sapply(stock_list, function(x){length(unique(x))}) %>% \ndata.table(colname = names(.), unique_values = .)","metadata":{"execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2022-04-30T02:43:32.297732Z","iopub.execute_input":"2022-04-30T02:43:32.299607Z","iopub.status.idle":"2022-04-30T02:43:32.874152Z"},"trusted":true},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"* We expect to predict price movements for some of the 4417 stocks in the total.\n* 全4417銘柄中のいくつかの銘柄について値動きを予測すると思われます。","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"**A brief comparison of old and new market segments.**  \n**新旧市場区分を簡単に比較します。**","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"code","source":"stock_list[, n := 1:.N, by = Section_Products]\nstock_list[n ==1] %>% select(4, 5)","metadata":{"execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2022-04-30T02:43:32.876777Z","iopub.execute_input":"2022-04-30T02:43:32.87834Z","iopub.status.idle":"2022-04-30T02:43:32.961657Z"},"trusted":true},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"* The new segments(4/4/2022-) seems simpler and easier to understand.\n* 新区分(2022/4/4から)のほうが単純でわかりやすそうです。","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"## stock_prices\n**First, check the dataset.**  ","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"code","source":"glimpse(stock_prices)","metadata":{"execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2022-04-30T02:43:32.964312Z","iopub.execute_input":"2022-04-30T02:43:32.966111Z","iopub.status.idle":"2022-04-30T02:43:34.049489Z"},"trusted":true},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"* This appears to be a pure record of price movement.\n* I will not mention \"Tatget\" for now.\n* これは純粋な値動きの記録のようです。\n* Tatgetについてはとりあえず触れません。","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"**How many stocks should we forecast?**","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"code","source":"length(stock_prices$SecuritiesCode %>% unique())","metadata":{"execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2022-04-30T02:43:34.051782Z","iopub.execute_input":"2022-04-30T02:43:34.053095Z","iopub.status.idle":"2022-04-30T02:43:34.598279Z"},"trusted":true},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"* The forecast covers 2,000 stocks out of 4,417 stocks.\n* 予測対象は4417銘柄のうち2000銘柄になります。","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"**Data period**","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"code","source":"stock_prices[, Date := as.IDate(Date)]\nrange(stock_prices$Date)","metadata":{"execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2022-04-30T02:43:34.600648Z","iopub.execute_input":"2022-04-30T02:43:34.602039Z","iopub.status.idle":"2022-04-30T02:43:34.698559Z"},"trusted":true},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"* All data are from the old market classification (Section_Products).\n* すべて旧市場分類時(Section_Products)のデータになります。","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"## financials\n**First, check the dataset.**  ","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"code","source":"glimpse(financials)","metadata":{"execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2022-04-30T02:43:34.700896Z","iopub.execute_input":"2022-04-30T02:43:34.702271Z","iopub.status.idle":"2022-04-30T02:43:34.758177Z"},"trusted":true},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"**Convert some strings into numerical.**  \n**Corrects time data to ITime.**  \n**いつくかの数値データが文字列になっているため変換します。**  \n**時刻データをITimeに修正します。**","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"code","source":"cols <- names(financials)[c(13:36, 43:45)]\nfinancials[, (cols) := lapply(.SD, as.numeric), .SDcols = cols]\nfinancials$DisclosedTime <- as.ITime(financials$DisclosedTime)","metadata":{"execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2022-04-30T02:43:34.760555Z","iopub.execute_input":"2022-04-30T02:43:34.761953Z","iopub.status.idle":"2022-04-30T02:43:35.363063Z"},"trusted":true},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"code","source":"glimpse(financials)","metadata":{"_kg_hide-output":true,"execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2022-04-30T02:43:35.365482Z","iopub.execute_input":"2022-04-30T02:43:35.366894Z","iopub.status.idle":"2022-04-30T02:43:35.406859Z"},"trusted":true},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"* It's worked!","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"**Check for unique value and NA.**  \n**ユニークバリューとNAをチェックします。**","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"code","source":"dt_tmp <- financials %>% sapply(function(x){length(unique(x))}) %>%\n  data.table(feature = names(.), unique_values = .)\n\ndt_tmp2 <- colSums(sapply(financials,is.na)) %>%\n  data.table(feature = names(.), NAs = .)\n\ncat(\"nrow = \", nrow(financials))\ndt_tmp <- dt_tmp %>% left_join(dt_tmp2, by = \"feature\")\ndt_tmp[, ColNo := .I]\ndt_tmp","metadata":{"_kg_hide-input":true,"execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2022-04-30T02:43:35.409155Z","iopub.execute_input":"2022-04-30T02:43:35.410433Z","iopub.status.idle":"2022-04-30T02:43:35.777817Z"},"trusted":true},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"**The following may be particularly relevant to stock price movements in this context.**\n1. EarningsPerShare\n1. ForecastEarningsPerShare\n1. DisclosedDate\n  \n* If the expected earnings per share is higher than the previous period, the stock price may rise in the future. Unfortunately, there seems to be a lot of NA.\n* Price movements are expected to be large on the disclosure date.\n\n**この中で株価の動きと特に関係が深そうなものは以下が考えられます。**  \n1. EarningsPerShare: 一株利益  \n1. ForecastEarningsPerShare: 予想一株利益  \n1. DisclosedDate: 開示日\n  \n* 予想一株利益が前期より上昇していれば今後の株価は上昇するかもしれません。残念ながらNAが多そうです。\n* 開示日には値動きが大きくなると思われます。","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"**The stock market closes at 3:00 p.m.**   \nWe believe that earnings disclosure after 3:00 p.m. has a greater impact on the next day than price movements on that day.  \nFor this reason, I will move the disclosure date by one day for earnings disclosures after 3:00 p.m.  \n**株式市場は15時に終了します。**  \n15時以降の業績開示は、当日の値動きよりも翌日への影響が大きいと考えます。  \nこのため、15時以降の業績開示は開示日を1日ずらしておきます。","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"code","source":"financials[DisclosedTime >= as.ITime(\"15:00:00\"), \n           DisclosedDate := DisclosedDate + 1]","metadata":{"execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2022-04-30T02:43:35.781605Z","iopub.execute_input":"2022-04-30T02:43:35.783169Z","iopub.status.idle":"2022-04-30T02:43:35.804169Z"},"trusted":true},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"**Change column name that is too long.**  \n**長すぎる列名称を変更します。**","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"code","source":"setnames(financials,\n         names(financials)[43], \"NumberOfIssued\")","metadata":{"execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2022-04-30T02:43:35.808616Z","iopub.execute_input":"2022-04-30T02:43:35.811281Z","iopub.status.idle":"2022-04-30T02:43:35.836864Z"},"trusted":true},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"**Consider missing value completion for ForecastEarningsPerShare.**  \nI believe earnings per share can be obtained by dividing earnings by the number of shares outstanding.  \n  \n**ForecastEarningsPerShareの欠損値補完を検討します。**  \n一株利益は、利益を発行済み株式数で割れば求まると思います。","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"code","source":"financials[, ForecastEarningsPerShare2 := round(ForecastProfit/NumberOfIssued, digits = 1)]","metadata":{"execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2022-04-30T02:43:35.839354Z","iopub.execute_input":"2022-04-30T02:43:35.841318Z","iopub.status.idle":"2022-04-30T02:43:35.863485Z"},"trusted":true},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"**Check to see if the value is available.**  \n**値が使用できそうか確認します。**","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"code","source":"financials[!is.na(ForecastEarningsPerShare)][!is.na(ForecastEarningsPerShare2)] %>%\n  select(ForecastEarningsPerShare, ForecastEarningsPerShare2) %>% head(10)","metadata":{"execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2022-04-30T02:43:35.866236Z","iopub.execute_input":"2022-04-30T02:43:35.86775Z","iopub.status.idle":"2022-04-30T02:43:35.928135Z"},"trusted":true},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"* Probably okay. The values are approximately similar.\n* たぶん大丈夫。だいたい似たような値になっています。","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"code","source":"financials[is.na(ForecastEarningsPerShare)\n          ][!is.na(ForecastEarningsPerShare2)] %>% nrow()","metadata":{"execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2022-04-30T02:43:35.932296Z","iopub.execute_input":"2022-04-30T02:43:35.934715Z","iopub.status.idle":"2022-04-30T02:43:35.963155Z"},"trusted":true},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"* 846 cases could be completed.It is not much, but I will interpolate.\n* 846件補完できそうです。ちょっと少ないですが補間しておきます。","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"code","source":"financials[is.na(ForecastEarningsPerShare), ForecastEarningsPerShare := ForecastEarningsPerShare2]","metadata":{"execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2022-04-30T02:43:35.96712Z","iopub.execute_input":"2022-04-30T02:43:35.969073Z","iopub.status.idle":"2022-04-30T02:43:35.984478Z"},"trusted":true},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"**Ceate Disclosed(1or0) when I combine them later.**  \n**あとで結合したときに決算開示日がわかるようにしておきます。**","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"code","source":"financials[, disclosed := 1]","metadata":{"execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2022-04-30T02:43:35.988153Z","iopub.execute_input":"2022-04-30T02:43:35.989793Z","iopub.status.idle":"2022-04-30T02:43:36.006139Z"},"trusted":true},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"## Combining Data Sets","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"**Let's combine the stock price data set with stock information and financial performance information.**  \n**株価データセットに、銘柄情報、業績情報を結合してみましょう。**","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"code","source":"dt_comb <- stock_prices %>% \n  left_join(stock_list %>% select(1,3:9), by = \"SecuritiesCode\")","metadata":{"execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2022-04-30T02:43:36.010056Z","iopub.execute_input":"2022-04-30T02:43:36.011695Z","iopub.status.idle":"2022-04-30T02:43:37.983251Z"},"trusted":true},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"code","source":"dt_comb <- \n  left_join(dt_comb, financials %>% select(4, 5, 17, 36, 47) %>% \n            rename(Date = DisclosedDate), by = c(\"Date\", \"SecuritiesCode\"))\ndt_comb[is.na(disclosed), disclosed := 0]\n\ndt_comb %>% head(5)","metadata":{"execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2022-04-30T02:43:37.987293Z","iopub.execute_input":"2022-04-30T02:43:37.988965Z","iopub.status.idle":"2022-04-30T02:43:40.202556Z"},"trusted":true},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"**Check the percentage of stocks in the Tokyo market that should be forecasted.**  \n  \n**東京市場の銘柄のうち、予測すべき銘柄の割合を確認してみます。**","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"code","source":"dt_tmp <- \n  stock_list %>% count(NewMarketSegment) %>% arrange(desc(n)) %>%\n  rename(stock_list = n)\n\ndt_tmp <- \n  dt_tmp %>% \n    left_join(dt_comb[, .N, by = .(NewMarketSegment, SecuritiesCode)\n    ][, .N, by = .(NewMarketSegment)], by = \"NewMarketSegment\") %>%\n      rename(stock_prices = N)\n\ndt_tmp[, rate :=round(stock_prices/stock_list, digits = 2)]\ndt_tmp","metadata":{"_kg_hide-input":true,"execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2022-04-30T02:43:40.20612Z","iopub.execute_input":"2022-04-30T02:43:40.207572Z","iopub.status.idle":"2022-04-30T02:43:40.523893Z"},"trusted":true},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"* It appears that about 90% of the current prime market (former TSE First Section) and 20% of the remaining market issues are covered.\n* 現プライム市場（旧東証一部）の9割程度、残りの市場銘柄は2割程度が対象のようです。","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"**Make sure that the 2,000 stocks to be forecasted are not biased among the 33 industries.**  \n**予測すべき2000銘柄が33業種の中で偏っていないか確認しておきます。**","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"code","source":"options(repr.plot.width = 15, repr.plot.height = 8)\n\ng1<-\n  dt_comb[, .N, by = .(SecuritiesCode, SectorName_33)][, .N, by = SectorName_33] %>%\n  ggplot(aes(x = reorder(SectorName_33, N), y = N))+\n  geom_bar(stat = \"identity\", fill = mycol[2], alpha = 0.5)+\n  coord_flip()+\n  labs(title = \"Sector of the forecasted stocks\", x = \"\")\n\ng2 <-\n  stock_list[, .N, by = .(SecuritiesCode, SectorName_33)][, .N, by = SectorName_33] %>%\n  ggplot(aes(x = reorder(SectorName_33, N), y = N))+\n  geom_bar(stat = \"identity\", fill = mycol[1], alpha = 0.5)+\n  coord_flip()+\n  labs(title = \"Sector of the Tokyo Market stocks\", x = \"\")\n\ng1 + g2","metadata":{"_kg_hide-input":true,"execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2022-04-30T02:43:40.526893Z","iopub.execute_input":"2022-04-30T02:43:40.528273Z","iopub.status.idle":"2022-04-30T02:43:41.604415Z"},"trusted":true},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"* About half of the stocks in each sector appear to be set as forecast stocks.The \"_\" in the graph on the right is considered an index issue.\n* 各セクターの銘柄数のおよそ半数程度が予測銘柄に設定されているようです。右のグラフの\"_\"は指数銘柄と思われます。","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"code","source":"range(dt_comb$Date)","metadata":{"execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2022-04-30T02:43:41.607453Z","iopub.execute_input":"2022-04-30T02:43:41.609007Z","iopub.status.idle":"2022-04-30T02:43:42.147387Z"},"trusted":true},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"**Make a table of correspondence between StockName_33 and StockCOde_33, to use it later.**  \n**あとで使うかもしれないので、StockName と StockCodeの対応表を作成しておきます。**","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"code","source":"sector_name_code_33 <-\n  dt_comb[, .N, by =.(SectorName_33, SectorCode_33)\n         ][order(-N)][, .(SectorName_33, SectorCode_33)]\nsector_name_code_33","metadata":{"_kg_hide-output":true,"execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2022-04-30T02:43:42.149852Z","iopub.execute_input":"2022-04-30T02:43:42.151276Z","iopub.status.idle":"2022-04-30T02:43:42.239407Z"},"trusted":true},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"code","source":"sector_name_code_17 <-\n  dt_comb[, .N, by =.(SectorName_17, SectorCode_17)\n         ][order(-N)][, .(SectorName_17, SectorCode_17)]\nsector_name_code_17","metadata":{"_kg_hide-output":true,"execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2022-04-30T02:43:42.241938Z","iopub.execute_input":"2022-04-30T02:43:42.24334Z","iopub.status.idle":"2022-04-30T02:43:42.326628Z"},"trusted":true},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"## Stock Charts","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"**Visualization is performed with a set of three charts.**  \n* The upper chart shows the forecasted earnings per share for the current period, the middle chart shows the stock price, and the lower chart shows the Target.  \n* The pink vertical line indicates the date of earnings disclosure.  \n\n**3枚のチャートを1組にして可視化をおこないます。**  \n* 上段は、今期の予想人株利益の予測値、中段は株価、下段はTargetです。  \n* ピンクの縦線は、業績開示日をあらわします。","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"code","source":"make_stock_chart <- function(code){\n    options(repr.plot.width = 15, repr.plot.height = 12)\n    \n    dt_tmp <- dt_comb[SecuritiesCode == code]\n    disclosed_date <- as.POSIXct(dt_tmp[disclosed == 1, Date])\n    \n    x_min <- \"2017-02-01\"\n    x_max <- \"2021-11-30\"\n    x_range <- c(as.POSIXct(x_min), as.POSIXct(x_max))\n    \n    TL <- paste0(dt_tmp$SecuritiesCode[1], \": \", \n                 dt_tmp$Name[1], \": \", \n                 dt_tmp$NewMarketSegment[1])\n    \n    g1 <- \n      dt_tmp[!is.na(ForecastEarningsPerShare)] %>% \n      mutate(DATE = as.POSIXct(Date)) %>%\n      ggplot(aes(x = DATE, y = ForecastEarningsPerShare))+\n      geom_point(alpha = 0.7)+\n      geom_line(color = \"darkgray\", alpha = 0.8)+\n      geom_vline(xintercept = disclosed_date, color = mycol[8], alpha = 0.5)+\n      scale_x_datetime(breaks = \"2 months\", date_labels = \"%Y-%m\", limits = x_range)+\n      theme(axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 90, hjust = 1))+\n      labs(titles = TL, x = \"\")\n    \n    g2 <-\n      dt_tmp[!is.na(Close)] %>% mutate(DATE = as.POSIXct(Date)) %>%\n      ggplot(aes(x = DATE, y = Close))+\n      geom_line(alpha = 0.7)+\n      geom_vline(xintercept = disclosed_date, linetype = \"dashed\",color = mycol[8], alpha = 0.7)+\n      scale_x_datetime(breaks = \"2 months\", date_labels = \"%Y-%m\", limits = x_range)+\n      theme(axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 90, hjust = 1))+\n      labs(titles = TL, x = \"\")\n    \n    g3<-\n      dt_tmp[SecuritiesCode == code][!is.na(Close)] %>% \n      mutate(DATE = as.POSIXct(Date)) %>%\n      ggplot(aes(x = DATE, y = Target))+\n      geom_line(alpha = 0.7)+\n      geom_vline(xintercept = disclosed_date, color = mycol[8], alpha = 0.5)+\n      scale_x_datetime(breaks = \"2 months\", date_labels = \"%Y-%m\", limits = x_range)+\n      scale_y_continuous(breaks = seq(-0.2, 0.2, 0.04), limits = c(-0.16, 0.16))+\n      theme(axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 90, hjust = 1))+\n      labs(titles = TL, x = \"\")\n    \n    return (g1/g2/g3 + plot_layout(height = c(2, 2, 4)))\n    \n}","metadata":{"_kg_hide-input":true,"execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2022-04-30T02:43:42.3291Z","iopub.execute_input":"2022-04-30T02:43:42.330423Z","iopub.status.idle":"2022-04-30T02:43:42.343329Z"},"trusted":true},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"**First, let's display one stock from each of the 10 sectors from the Plum Market (formerly the First Section).**  \n**まずはプラム市場（旧東証一部）の17のセクターから1銘柄ずつ表示してみます。**","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"code","source":"sect = sector_name_code_17[,SectorCode_17]\ncode_gra <- vector()\n\nfor (c in sect){\n    num <- \n      dt_comb[NewMarketSegment == \"Prime Market\"][SectorCode_17 == c\n             ][, .N, SecuritiesCode][order(SecuritiesCode)][,SecuritiesCode][10]\n    code_gra <-  code_gra %>% append(num)\n}","metadata":{"_kg_hide-input":true,"execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2022-04-30T02:43:42.345896Z","iopub.execute_input":"2022-04-30T02:43:42.347308Z","iopub.status.idle":"2022-04-30T02:43:50.63531Z"},"trusted":true},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"code","source":"for (num in code_gra){\n    g <- make_stock_chart(num)\n    plot(g)\n}","metadata":{"_kg_hide-input":true,"execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2022-04-30T02:43:50.637706Z","iopub.execute_input":"2022-04-30T02:43:50.639107Z","iopub.status.idle":"2022-04-30T02:44:04.490513Z"},"trusted":true},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"I think the following can be mentioned.  \n* I thought that forecast earnings per share would be a leading indicator of stock price movement, but it seems to be a coincident indicator. If earnings per share is flat, the stock price is flat or declining, and if earnings per share is rising, the stock price is also rising.  \n* **Target value often moves significantly around the date of disclosure of earnings.** Financial results should be disclosed every three months. Others are considered earnings revisions (it is impossible to predict when they will be).\n* Sometimes the stock price suddenly halves or doubles, but this may be due to a stock split or capital increase. It seems that Target is calculated taking this into account.\n\n以下のような事がいえると思います。  \n* 予想一株利益は株価の動きの先行指標になると考えましたが、一致指標のようです。予想一株利益利益が下落傾向なら株価は下落傾向、横ばいなら株価は横ばいか下落傾向、上昇傾向なら株価も上昇傾向になります。  \n* **業績開示日の付近で、Target値が大きくふれるケースが多くみられます。**業績は3か月毎に開示されるはずです。その他は業績修正と思われます（いつあるかは予測不可能）。\n* 時々株価が急に半分や倍になるケースがありますがこれは、株式分割や増資の影響と思われます。Targetは、そこを考慮して計算されているように思います。","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"同じようにStandardとGrowthもみてみます。","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"code","source":"sect = sector_name_code_17[,SectorCode_17]\ncode_gra <- vector()\n\nfor (c in sect){\n    num <- \n      dt_comb[NewMarketSegment == \"Standard Market\"][SectorCode_17 == c\n             ][, .N, SecuritiesCode][order(SecuritiesCode)][,SecuritiesCode][5]\n    code_gra <-  code_gra %>% append(num)\n}\n\ncode_gra <- code_gra[!is.na(code_gra)]","metadata":{"_kg_hide-input":true,"execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2022-04-30T02:44:04.494428Z","iopub.execute_input":"2022-04-30T02:44:04.496713Z","iopub.status.idle":"2022-04-30T02:44:05.981948Z"},"trusted":true},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"**Standard Market**","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"code","source":"for (num in code_gra[1:5]){\n    g <- make_stock_chart(num)\n    plot(g)\n}","metadata":{"_kg_hide-input":true,"execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2022-04-30T02:44:05.985636Z","iopub.execute_input":"2022-04-30T02:44:05.987224Z","iopub.status.idle":"2022-04-30T02:44:10.133222Z"},"trusted":true},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"code","source":"sect = sector_name_code_17[,SectorCode_17]\ncode_gra <- vector()\n\nfor (c in sect){\n    num <- \n      dt_comb[NewMarketSegment == \"Growth Market\"][SectorCode_17 == c\n             ][, .N, SecuritiesCode][order(SecuritiesCode)][,SecuritiesCode][2]\n    code_gra <-  code_gra %>% append(num)\n}\n\ncode_gra <- code_gra[!is.na(code_gra)]","metadata":{"_kg_hide-input":true,"execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2022-04-30T02:44:10.135702Z","iopub.execute_input":"2022-04-30T02:44:10.137106Z","iopub.status.idle":"2022-04-30T02:44:11.194882Z"},"trusted":true},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"**Growth Market**","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"code","source":"for (num in code_gra){\n    g <- make_stock_chart(num)\n    plot(g)\n}","metadata":{"_kg_hide-input":true,"execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2022-04-30T02:44:11.197471Z","iopub.execute_input":"2022-04-30T02:44:11.198962Z","iopub.status.idle":"2022-04-30T02:44:17.292399Z"},"trusted":true},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"* **Growth market stocks have large Target amplitudes.**\n* **Growthマーケットの銘柄はTargetの振幅が大きいです。**","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"### Other possible hypotheses that might affect Target's fluctuations include the following, which I would like to examine.　  \n* When the moving average divergence of the stock price increases, Target will swing in the opposite direction at some point.\n* If the stock price is in an uptrend, Target is more likely to swing to the positive side, and if the stock price is in a downtrend, Target is more likely to swing to the negative side.\n* When the ratio of days when Close is positive compared to the previous day increases, Target will swing to the negative at a certain point, and when the ratio of days when Close is negative compared to the previous day increases, Target will swing to the positive at a certain point (influence of psychological indicators).\n* Stocks in the same industry will have similar movements (stocks with similar stock codes will have similar movements).\n\n### その他、Targetの変動に影響しそうな以下の仮説が考えられ、検証してみたいと考えています。　  \n* 移動平均乖離率が高くなると、ある時点で逆方向への動きが大きくなる。\n* 株価が上昇トレンドならTargetはブラスに下落トレンドならTargetはマイナスに振れやすくなる。\n* Closeが前日比プラスの日の割合が多くなると、ある時点でTargetはマイナスに振れ、Closeが前日比マイナスの日の割合が多くなると、ある時点でTargetはプラスに振れる（サイコロジカル指数の影響）。\n* 同業種の銘柄は同じような動きになる（株式コードが近い銘柄は同じような動きになる）。","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"## Appendix\n### Study on stock splits\n\nI am curious about the stock split and will check the data.  \n株式分割について気になったので、データを確認してみます。","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"code","source":"make_stock_chart2 <- function(code){\n    options(repr.plot.width = 15, repr.plot.height = 8)\n    \n    dt_tmp <- dt_comb[SecuritiesCode == code]\n    disclosed_date <- as.POSIXct(dt_tmp[disclosed == 1, Date])\n    \n    x_min <- \"2017-02-01\"\n    x_max <- \"2021-11-30\"\n    x_range <- c(as.POSIXct(x_min), as.POSIXct(x_max))\n    \n    TL <- paste0(dt_tmp$SecuritiesCode[1], \": \", \n                 dt_tmp$Name[1], \": \", \n                 dt_tmp$NewMarketSegment[1])\n       \n    g2 <-\n      dt_tmp[!is.na(Close)] %>% mutate(DATE = as.POSIXct(Date)) %>%\n      ggplot(aes(x = DATE, y = Close))+\n      geom_line(alpha = 0.7)+\n      geom_vline(xintercept = disclosed_date, linetype = \"dashed\",color = mycol[8], alpha = 0.7)+\n      scale_x_datetime(breaks = \"2 months\", date_labels = \"%Y-%m\", limits = x_range)+\n      theme(axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 90, hjust = 1))+\n      labs(titles = TL, x = \"\")\n    \n    g3<-\n      dt_tmp[SecuritiesCode == code][!is.na(Close)] %>% \n      mutate(DATE = as.POSIXct(Date)) %>%\n      ggplot(aes(x = DATE, y = Target))+\n      geom_line(alpha = 0.7)+\n      geom_vline(xintercept = disclosed_date, color = mycol[8], alpha = 0.5)+\n      scale_x_datetime(breaks = \"2 months\", date_labels = \"%Y-%m\", limits = x_range)+\n      scale_y_continuous(breaks = seq(-0.2, 0.2, 0.04), limits = c(-0.16, 0.16))+\n      theme(axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 90, hjust = 1))+\n      labs(titles = TL, x = \"\")\n    \n      g2/g3#return (g1/g2/g3 + plot_layout(height = c(2, 2, 4)))\n}","metadata":{"_kg_hide-input":true},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"**Example: SecuritiesCode == 2153**  \n\nAs shown in the chart below, the stock price was halved in November 2020.  \nHowever, Target seems to be calculated properly.  \n下のチャートのように2020年11月に株価が半分になっています。  \nしかし、Targetはちゃんと計算されているようです。","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"code","source":"make_stock_chart2(code= 2153)","metadata":{},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"code","source":"stock_prices[SecuritiesCode == 2153\n             ][Date > as.IDate(\"2020-11-20\") & Date < as.IDate(\"2020-12-01\")]","metadata":{},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"* The stock price has been halved since 2020-11-27. The stock's website confirms that there was a stock split.\n* AdjustmentFactor on 2020-11-26 is 0.5.\n* I think that Target is calculated as follows.  \n(Close_shift2-Close_shift1 x AdjustmentFactor)/(Close_shift1 x AdjustmentFactor)\n* _  \n* 2020-11-27から株価が半分になっています。銘柄のホームページをみると株式分割があったことが確認できました。\n* 2020-11-26のAdjustmentFactorが0.5になっています。\n* Targetは以下のように計算していると考えます。  \n(Close_shift2-Close_shift1 x AdjustmentFactor)/(Close_shift1 x AdjustmentFactor)","metadata":{}}]}